cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI 

The paper deals with using deep convolutional neural networks to predict language recovery post-stroke using MRI scans. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of neural networks also suggests the involvement of neural networks (cs.NE) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with predicting outcomes, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
